    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "T6RW5",
      "x": 40,
      "y": 640,
      "name": "annot",
      "fill": "#333333",
      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
      "width": 1100,
      "content": "KEY CHANGES — (1) Pill now LEADS the band (above Back-to-menu), with pt-3 on the leading element. (2) Closed pill face shows workspace NAME + repo NAME subtitle (e.g. jikig-ai/soleur); the Owner/Member ROLE is no longer on the face. (3) Role moves INTO the dropdown, shown per-membership row (Owner · 2 members). (4) Solo users get the same name+repo chip, non-interactive (no ▾). (5) Standalone 'Working on:' row is REMOVED — its repo string now lives in the pill. (6) Collapsed md:w-14 column is UNCHANGED (no room for a subtitle): back arrow, avatar mark, repo dot, section glyph. The J5 revocation interstitial (not shown) still renders above the band when fellBackToSolo.",
      "lineHeight": 1.5,
      "fontFamily": "Inter",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontWeight": "normal"
    }
